edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos

Class PaxosAcceptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.PaxosAcceptor

  • public class PaxosAcceptor
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    V. Arun This class is a paxos acceptor and manages all acceptor state. It has no public methods, only protected methods, as it is expected to be used *only* by PaxosInstanceStateMachine. Every PaxosInstanceStateMachine has a PaxosAcceptorState object, whether or not the paxos group is processing any requests. This object contributes to about 90B of space.
